## Project Summary

This project is a React-based web application that serves as a marketplace for buying and selling books. It provides users with a platform to discover, purchase, and sell books online. Users can browse through a wide selection of books, view book details, add them to their shopping cart, and complete purchases. Additionally, users can create seller accounts, list their own books for sale, manage their inventory, and process transactions
